Description:
============

Acronis True Image - an integrated software package that provides the security of all information on your computer. True Image allows you to backup the operating system, applications, user settings and all of your data, while also securely destroying any confidential data you no longer need. C using this software, you can back up selected files and folders, settings, and e-mails Microsoft customers, and even entire drives and selected sections. Online Storage lets you store your most important files in the remote repository. Your data will be protected even in the event of loss, theft or destruction of the computer. Acronis Nonstop Backup periodically (every five minutes) saves the changes that have occurred in the system and files that, if necessary, makes it easy to return to at any time.

System Requirements (Supported):
--------------------------------

    Windows XP SP3
    Windows 7 SP1 (all editions)
    Windows 8 (all editions)
    Windows 8.1 (all editions)
    Windows 10 (all editions)
    Windows Home Server 2011

Not Supported:
--------------

Windows XP x64


Hardware Requirements:
----------------------

    1 GB of RAM
    Pentium processor with a clock speed of at least 1 GHz
    1.5 GB of available hard disk space

Supported file systems:
-----------------------

    NTFS
    FAT32
    Ext2 / Ext3 / Ext4
    ReiserFS
    Linux SWAP
    File system Ext2 / Ext3 / Ext4, ReiserFS, and Linux SWAP only supported operations
    backup or restore on drives or partitions.
